title: Blondshell returns to Live on KEXP with a performance of "T&A" and more

author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Blondshell performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded June 4, 2025.

23's A Baby 00:38
Toy 04:43
Event Of A Fire 09:07
T&A 13:11

Sabrina Teitelbaum - Vocals
Kerri Stewart - Guitar

Anna Crane - Drums
